### About:
I am a Software Engineer that graduated from Florida Institute of Technology in 2016. I am interested in Java Development, Software Testing, Windows Development, Game Development, and programming in general. 

Some of my skills include Java, C++, C#. I am knowledgeable with Linux and Windows systems and have worked with databases such as MySQL. I am comfortable using Git, Visual Studio, and Eclipse.
